Method comparison

run on krak

require(ThesisRpackage)
G.file <- "~/Projects/Thesis/Data/1000Genomes/Phase3Chrm22/European_Chrm22.maf.05.rds" ## run all simulation on the same 10000 loci sample
exp <- Article3_MethodComparison(G.file,
                                 outlier.props = c(0.01, 0.05, 0.1),
                                 n = NULL, L = 10000,
                                 K = 4,
                                 cs = c(0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8),
                                 nb.rep = 10,
                                 fast.only = FALSE,
                                 cluster.nb = 16,
                                 save = TRUE, bypass = FALSE)
